  <entry>
    <title>数据结构与算法</title>
    <link href="https://flyfish567.github.io/posts/4b0178e0.html"/>
    <id>https://flyfish567.github.io/posts/4b0178e0.html</id>
    <published>2025-02-15T03:26:16.896Z</published>
    <updated>2025-02-24T15:29:38.213Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="前序"><a href="#前序" class="headerlink" title="前序"></a>前序</h2><h3 id="时间复杂度"><a href="#时间复杂度" class="headerlink" title="时间复杂度"></a>时间复杂度</h3><p>T(n)=O(f(n))</p><p><img src="https://flyfish567.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/web.imgimage-20250215114316774.png" alt="image-20250215114316774"></p><h3 id="空间复杂度"><a href="#空间复杂度" class="headerlink" title="空间复杂度"></a>空间复杂度</h3><p><img src="https://flyfish567.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/web.imgimage-20250215144346998.png" alt="image-20250215144346998"></p><h2 id="线性表"><a href="#线性表" class="headerlink" title="线性表"></a>线性表</h2><h3 id="定义与特点"><a href="#定义与特点" class="headerlink" title="定义与特点"></a>定义与特点</h3><p><strong>线性表：由n个数据特性相同（相同数据类型）的元素构成的有限序列</strong></p><h3 id="顺序表示与实现"><a href="#顺序表示与实现" class="headerlink" title="顺序表示与实现"></a>顺序表示与实现</h3><p><img src="https://flyfish567.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/web.imgimage-20250215150657540.png" alt="image-20250215150657540"></p><h4 id="初始化"><a href="#初始化" class="headerlink" title="初始化"></a><strong>初始化</strong></h4><p><img src="https://flyfish567.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/web.imgimage-20250215152409683.png" alt="image-20250215152409683"></p><h4 id="动态分配内存地址初始化"><a href="#动态分配内存地址初始化" class="headerlink" title="动态分配内存地址初始化"></a><strong>动态分配内存地址初始化</strong></h4><p><img src="https://flyfish567.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/web.imgimage-20250215214316665.png" alt="image-20250215214316665"></p><h4 id="添加"><a href="#添加" class="headerlink" title="添加"></a><strong>添加</strong></h4><p><img src="https://flyfish567.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/web.imgimage-20250215152902712.png" alt="image-20250215152902712"></p><h4 id="遍历"><a href="#遍历" class="headerlink" title="遍历"></a><strong>遍历</strong></h4><p><img src="https://flyfish567.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/web.imgimage-20250215155238680.png" alt="image-20250215155238680"></p><h4 id="插入"><a href="#插入" class="headerlink" title="插入"></a><strong>插入</strong></h4><p><img src="https://flyfish567.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/web.imgimage-20250215160901097.png" alt="image-20250215160901097"></p><h4 id="删除"><a href="#删除" class="headerlink" title="删除"></a><strong>删除</strong></h4><p><img src="https://flyfish567.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/web.imgimage-20250215212537775.png" alt="image-20250215212537775"></p><h4 id="查找"><a href="#查找" class="headerlink" title="查找"></a><strong>查找</strong></h4><p><img src="https://flyfish567.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/web.imgimage-20250215213358500.png" alt="image-20250215213358500"></p><h3 id="链式表示与实现"><a href="#链式表示与实现" class="headerlink" title="链式表示与实现"></a>链式表示与实现</h3><h4 id="定义"><a href="#定义" class="headerlink" title="定义"></a><strong>定义</strong></h4><p><img src="https://flyfish567.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/web.imgimage-20250215214809236.png" alt="image-20250215214809236"></p><h4 id="结构"><a href="#结构" class="headerlink" title="结构"></a><strong>结构</strong></h4><p><img src="https://flyfish567.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/web.imgimage-20250215215713387.png" alt="image-20250215215713387"></p><h4 id="初始化-1"><a href="#初始化-1" class="headerlink" title="初始化"></a><strong>初始化</strong></h4><p><img src="https://flyfish567.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/web.imgimage-20250215221334935.png" alt="image-20250215221334935"></p><h4 id="插入：头插法"><a href="#插入：头插法" class="headerlink" title="插入：头插法"></a><strong>插入：头插法</strong></h4><p><img src="https://flyfish567.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/web.imgimage-20250217155438126.png" alt="image-20250217155438126"></p><p><img src="https://flyfish567.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/web.imgimage-20250215222622737.png" alt="image-20250215222622737"></p><h4 id="尾插法"><a href="#尾插法" class="headerlink" title="尾插法"></a>尾插法</h4><p><strong>获取尾节点</strong></p><p><img src="https://flyfish567.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/web.imgimage-20250217160537755.png" alt="image-20250217160537755"></p><p><strong>插入</strong></p><p><img src="https://flyfish567.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/web.imgimage-20250217160610370.png" alt="image-20250217160610370"></p><h4 id="在指定位置插入"><a href="#在指定位置插入" class="headerlink" title="在指定位置插入"></a>在指定位置插入</h4><p><img src="https://flyfish567.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/web.imgimage-20250217161053539.png" alt="image-20250217161053539"></p><h4 id="删除-1"><a href="#删除-1" class="headerlink" title="删除"></a>删除</h4><p><img src="https://flyfish567.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/web.imgimage-20250217162427585.png" alt="image-20250217162427585"></p><p><img src="https://flyfish567.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/web.imgimage-20250217162634916.png" alt="image-20250217162634916"></p><h4 id="遍历-1"><a href="#遍历-1" class="headerlink" title="遍历"></a>遍历</h4><p><img src="https://flyfish567.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/web.imgimage-20250217155737990.png" alt="image-20250217155737990"></p><h4 id="获取链表长度"><a href="#获取链表长度" class="headerlink" title="获取链表长度"></a>获取链表长度</h4><p><img src="C:\Users\FLYFISH\AppData\Roaming\Typora\typora-user-images\image-20250217163534134.png" alt="image-20250217163534134"></p><h4 id="释放链表"><a href="#释放链表" class="headerlink" title="释放链表"></a>释放链表</h4><p><img src="https://flyfish567.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/web.imgimage-20250217164130296.png" alt="image-20250217164130296">                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                               </p><p><img src="https://flyfish567.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/web.imgimage-20250217164144949.png" alt="image-20250217164144949"></p><h4 id="反转链表"><a href="#反转链表" class="headerlink" title="反转链表"></a>反转链表</h4><p><img src="https://flyfish567.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/web.imgimage-20250224220315141.png" alt="image-20250224220315141"></p><p><img src="https://flyfish567.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/web.imgimage-20250224221320778.png" alt="image-20250224221320778"></p><h4 id="删除中间节点"><a href="#删除中间节点" class="headerlink" title="删除中间节点"></a>删除中间节点</h4><p><img src="https://flyfish567.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/web.imgimage-20250224221607205.png" alt="image-20250224221607205"></p><p><img src="https://flyfish567.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/web.imgimage-20250224222113960.png" alt="image-20250224222113960"></p><h4 id="技巧"><a href="#技巧" class="headerlink" title="技巧"></a>技巧</h4><ol><li>快慢指针</li></ol><h4 id="单向循坏链表"><a href="#单向循坏链表" class="headerlink" title="单向循坏链表"></a>单向循坏链表</h4><p><img src="https://flyfish567.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/web.imgimage-20250224230347580.png" alt="image-20250224230347580"></p><h5 id="判断链表是否是循坏链表"><a href="#判断链表是否是循坏链表" class="headerlink" title="判断链表是否是循坏链表"></a>判断链表是否是循坏链表</h5><p>使用快慢指针，当两个指针相遇时，存在环，返回1；若直到两个指针都为空，那么不存在，返回0</p><p><img src="https://flyfish567.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/web.imgimage-20250224230939154.png" alt="image-20250224230939154"></p>]]></content>
    
    
      
      
